quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  7,1,"Alif,\tLaam,\tMiiym,\tSwaad.\t(Insiguro\tyizi\tndome\thamwe\tn’uwufise ubumenyi bwazo zose n’Imana yonyene gusa)"
  7,2,"N’igitabu camanuwe kuri wewe, kandi ntugire amazinda k’umuzirikanyi wawe, kugira ngo ushobore gutuza ugikoresheje, kandi kibe arico ushikirizako ubutumwa ku bantu bemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri"
  7,3,"Nimukurikire ivyo mwamanuriwe bivuye ku Muremyi wanyu, kandi ntimukurikire abo mwizeye yuko aribo babakingiye aho kwizera Imana, ivyo navyo nibikeyi cane mwibuka"
  7,4,N’ibisagara bingahe twahoneje n’igihe hashika ibihano vyacu mw’ijoro canke mugihe co k’umutaga nabo basinziriye
  7,5,"Rero nticari ikigandaro cabo mugihe bashikirwa n’ibihano vyacu atari uko bavuga bati:- ntankeka twebwe twari twarahemukiye imitima yacu"
  7,6,"Mu vy’ukuri tuzoba baza bamwe barungikirwa intumwa z’Imana, duteko tubabaze iyo bajanywe"
  7,7,"Kandi tuzobabwira k’ubumenyi bwacu muvyo bagize, kandi ntitwari kure yabo mugire babigira"
  7,8,"Kuri uwo musi igipimo kizoba kingana, rero abazoba bafise uburemere buremeye cane abo nibo bazoba bafise intsinzi nyakuri"
  7,9,Nayo abazoba bafise uburemere buhwahutse abo nibo bataye mukaga imitima yabo kubera ubwishime bw’aya majambo matagatifu y’Imana
  7,10,"Mu vy’ukuri twaraba tsimbataje kuri iy’Isi, kandi twaraba shiriyemwo ibikenewe mu buzima bwanyu, rero n’ikenguruka rikeyi gusa mukenguruka"
  7,11,"Mu vy’ukuri twarabaremye hanyuma tubashirira ho amashusho, hanyuma tubwira abamarayika duti:- nimupfukamire intumwa y’Imana Adamu (iii), baca barapfukama bose dukuyemwo uwitwa Ibilisi yavumwe niwe atari mubapfukamye"